Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到小文了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.61,0:00:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美歌真像个男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  美歌女孩子气十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们二人同体呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.49,0:00:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽  通过认证
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 很疼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西很危险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以把这种东西对着别人哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌  要不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医…医生  救护车…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:03:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫医生没用的  医院也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是你女儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  他是美川煌老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开  给我打开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怂恿我们家文歌的是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报上名字来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要全名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  对不起  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您在此稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被炒啦  小心我让你在这行混不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  嘴角
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  反正我本来就不被看好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何  我不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况  医生看了肯定会引起大骚乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  美川她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可被打中了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是叫救护车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杖在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是杖啦  是卡娜卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总比通报到上面  事情闹大了好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克…风？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是杖在说话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧  这个卡娜卡是活的还可以说话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能理解我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.23,0:05:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于你的事  还有其它的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于长大的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指文伽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长大的邮递员  还能有其他人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮递员都是死者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以时间保持停止  成长也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以永远也不会死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说和我们不同  那孩子的年龄和外表相符
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说她还是个孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做邮递员还早得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经是一个叫做美川文歌的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  可是医院里的那孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  三年前开始一直昏迷  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好听文歌说到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说完后再提问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续吧  文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父亲是美川煌  刚才朝我开枪的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我出生后立刻和父亲离婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱泽美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女演员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和名字一样  是个美女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在应该和别人结婚了  住在海外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我不知道妈妈爱泽美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲  美川煌抚养我长大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌  吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  做得很容易入口了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  爸爸  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你  啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌曾经是个温柔的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我曾经最喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也爱着身为分身的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌  是上艺术课的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不记得何时  为什么开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后的世界如同冰雪的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何活物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有草  没有花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有四季  什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  死后的世界是美丽的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被统一的简单颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有虫  没有细菌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何污垢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终极洁净  无垢  干净
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}绮丽(kirei)在日语中有『干净』和『美丽』意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干净?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是美丽的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽  竟说是美丽的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肮脏的黑色眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚荣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  背叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌老师为什么要做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,底稿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌  无数次地用我的身体写底稿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归纳构思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很讨厌  很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我并不知道煌之外的父亲是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如冰雪般透明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如罪孽般美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  讨厌  讨厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}我  最喜欢的  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,污秽的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我的面前  消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻底消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温柔的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:10:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能做这种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.66,0:11:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  不是的  不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  我诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双重…人格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  明明有两个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个在医院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  你是死后文的邮递员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是美歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃出来的那重人格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的事情全部推给小文  狡猾的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  是个坏孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是咧  小文是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.93,0:12:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  谢谢  美歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文  洗完澡  画城堡的画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡里有王子和公主  晚上有舞会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有猫小丑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有  还有猫头鹰家庭教师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢食蚁兽女仆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她是个贪吃鬼  总是被甩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上唯一的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河马军队都是贪吃鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都吃  什么都喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢河马国  感谢河马国
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家分给我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌老师一直在虐待自己的女儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑子坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么作家  都是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系  那样写出的书卖了80万册啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才把丑闻掩盖下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真干得出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们毕竟是出版社嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  还有点疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人注意到吗  文歌…你们的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不被允许出家门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没见过煌以外的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至不知道幼儿园  小学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中是第一所学校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次  被很多人注视
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一天到晚待在保健室里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…不全是恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人群中  心会疲劳  会紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小文仍然努力呆在学校里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为喜欢学校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  你是美歌对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去学校的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.61,0:15:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在脑海的深处注视着她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝你的事也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是因为小文讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是吓了一跳  不由得…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下可好了  要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经是初中时的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是因为在意  才这么拚命找美川吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说姐姐  稍微说下你妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦斯爆炸？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不要丢下我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要好好惩罚她不可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用哪个好  用哪个好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.28,0:16:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用哪个好  真难选
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌  文歌  文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从里面锁上的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川  美川
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢打我  明明那样爱过你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:18:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被那样虐待  小文到最后一刻依然喜欢着你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要背叛我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把『美丽』从你体内赶出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文会死的 小文会死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}好痛  好痛啊  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文会死的…小文
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再欺负小文了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.52,0:19:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射杀你的不是小文  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小文深信是自己干的  封闭了心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经连我的声音都听不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该把制裁你的事情交给小文的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在就去死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是杀了人类  是瞒不过福音局的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁管那些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文有多喜欢你  我就多恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文无法下手  我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文  小文她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡  你们的工作要是被警察知道了会很麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  警察啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没法解释我们的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这个人工作  赚取文歌的住院费
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我也想继续看这个无药可救的美川煌写的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么老师  您会写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我没有文歌的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不写  我们会很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我努力过了  可是写不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别撒娇了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了一惊  夏香的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她关键时刻很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然会做到那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到那样的文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后不可以有事瞒着我了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是搭档啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了等待那边的文歌  文伽成了邮递员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地选这片送信区域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我们约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我们能不能和你一起等呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你喜欢文歌一样  我们也很喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也很喜欢她  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  大家


